      <p class="mt-7 max-w-3xl text-xl text-cyan-100">Mobile-first cart recovery specialization. In a full marketing command center, Recart is evaluated on stack fit — capture, lifecycle, SMS, reviews, loyalty, merchandising, analytics — not logo familiarity alone.</p>
      <p class="mt-5 max-w-3xl text-lg text-slate-300">Rating: ★ {app.rating} · Pricing: Paid plans / custom · Shopify depth: {app.shopifyDepth} · Automation: {app.automationDepth}</p>
      <div class="mt-9 flex flex-wrap gap-3"><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/compare/sequenzy-vs-klaviyo">Stack battlecards</a><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/guides/stack-architecture">Stack architecture</a></div>
    </div>
