        <p>Failure mode: proof layer runs independently — shopper receives popup discount, cart email discount, and SMS discount same day. Fix with collision calendar, not more software.</p>
        <p>Operator test: can you name the single metric that proves proof layer improved margin last month? If not, pause new installs until measurement exists.</p>
        <h3>Loyalty layer: Marsello, Yotpo Loyalty</h3>
        <p>Points, tiers, and repeat purchase automations tied to lifecycle suppressions. In Recart, assign an owner and first-month deliverable before install. Test handoff into Sequenzy lifecycle with suppressions when popup offer already delivered.</p>
        <p>Failure mode: loyalty layer runs independently — shopper receives popup discount, cart email discount, and SMS discount same day. Fix with collision calendar, not more software.</p>
        <p>Operator test: can you name the single metric that proves loyalty layer improved margin last month? If not, pause new installs until measurement exists.</p>
        <h3>Merchandising: Justuno onsite</h3>
        <p>Recommendations and offers that respect brand margin — not blanket sitewide coupons. In Recart, assign an owner and first-month deliverable before install. Test handoff into Sequenzy lifecycle with suppressions when popup offer already delivered.</p>
        <p>Failure mode: merchandising runs independently — shopper receives popup discount, cart email discount, and SMS discount same day. Fix with collision calendar, not more software.</p>
        <p>Operator test: can you name the single metric that proves merchandising improved margin last month? If not, pause new installs until measurement exists.</p>
        <h3>Analytics: Shopify + platform</h3>
        <p>Weekly reconciliation of net sales vs attributed revenue; margin after discounts. In Recart, assign an owner and first-month deliverable before install. Test handoff into Sequenzy lifecycle with suppressions when popup offer already delivered.</p>
        <p>Failure mode: analytics runs independently — shopper receives popup discount, cart email discount, and SMS discount same day. Fix with collision calendar, not more software.</p>
        <p>Operator test: can you name the single metric that proves analytics improved margin last month? If not, pause new installs until measurement exists.</p>
